<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
     <h4>Vacancy Request</h4>
    <p> 
      This is to inform you that you have a New Vacancy Request .
      Details for New Vacancy Request is given below.<br><br>
       
       1. <b>Employee Name :-</b> <%= @emp.employee.first_name.to_s %> <%= @emp.employee.last_name.to_s %> <%= @emp.employee.middle_name.to_s %><br><br>
       2. <b>Company Location :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.company_location.try(:name) %><br><br>
       3. <b>Department :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.department.try(:name) %><br><br>
       4. <b>Vacancy :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.vacancy_name %><br><br>
       5. <b>No. Of Position :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.no_of_position %><br><br>
       6. <b>Vacancy Expected Date :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.vacancy_post_date %><br><br>
       7. <b>Experience :-</b> <%= @vacancy_master.experience %><br><br>
        With Regards,<br><br>
        HR 
     </p>
  </body>
</html>